{"tid":420083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國慶應定於8月29日","createTime":"2017-10-01T05:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T08:42:40.000Z","uid":35870,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"973e5975c255834024ea3e46f38901e67a725fa3","tid":420083,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"1842年8月29日，南京條約簽定，香港正式步入現代化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自由嘅大英帝國以武力擊敗封閉嘅清帝國，解救廣東沿岸一眾受盡清帝同林則徐壓迫嘅百姓<br />\n<br />\n香港從此成為遠東最自由嘅海港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912f53a54bd064bd0b39aaf6459cee7fbb132e9e","tid":420083,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f8/The_Signing_of_the_Treaty_of_Nanking.jpg/1920px-The_Signing_of_the_Treaty_of_Nanking.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff8%2FThe_Signing_of_the_Treaty_of_Nanking.jpg%2F1920px-The_Signing_of_the_Treaty_of_Nanking.jpg&h=824d3a5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d40aefd151f5715e4462fcfb61ec2342ee3fdcf","tid":420083,"uid":112769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:00:43.000Z","msg":"我死前<br />\n唔知有冇幸見證到<br />\n屬於香港人的網球場宣言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf36e99507f593b8c7a07fab1b3d0c3c5fb5d0c","tid":420083,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我死前<br />\n唔